Customer Service Forms





















 








Welcome to Customer Service Forms



















































This page offers you quick access to all of John Hancock’s customer service forms in one convenient location. To begin, click on the arrow below, then make a selection from the drop-down list.


   Choose...
   When you want to request a(n)...


 "Online Forms" 
After completing the online form(s), you will have two options - e-Sign and e-Submit the form(s) to John Hancock, or print, sign and mail to John Hancock.



Address change
Beneficiary change
Dividend withdrawal request
Name change
Ownership change
Policy loan request




Pre-authorized payment plan change
Request for lost policy
Request for policy change (no underwriting required)
Request to give 3rd party authorization
IRS W9 form




 "Claims & Other Forms"
These forms are fillable (i.e.,they can be completed electronically and then printed), or they can be printed and completed by hand. Mail the completed, signed form(s) to John Hancock.



Collateral assignment/release of collateral assignment
Electronic funds transfer information
Instructions on completing request for the Investment option changes
Instructions on completing request for transfer and allocation changes - Indexed UL
Option selection for matured policies
Partial withdrawal/partial surrender
Partnership statement
Policy surrender




Policy surrender settlement flyer
POA affidavit
Reinstatement application
Request for policy change (requiring underwriting)
Request for systematic withdrawal payments
Request for VUL TargetTrack change or cancellation
Request to use policy values to pay premiums
Successor owner agreement
Trust certification








 









